      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ")",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Shall be an astonishment to every one that passeth by it.—Every one that passeth by it shall be astonished: πᾶς ὁ διαπορευόμενος αὐτὸν ἐκστήσεται, LXX. Syriac, “Every one that passeth by it shall stop and shake his head, and sway with his hand, and say “. . . Kings adds, “and shall hiss” (certainly original).",
        "children": [
